 possibility of\nexploring the effects of mean-field anisotropy in collisions, without the\npenalty of computational cost behind the folding parametrization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Dec 2012 19:11:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Jan 2013 14:27:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 22 Aug 2013 11:41:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-23"}
