O\ntotal energy}. In general, our variational energy agrees in two-three-four\nsignificant digits with the most accurate results available at present as well\nas major expectation values.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Dec 2012 01:35:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Apr 2013 17:56:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
